examples.en: The plant absorbs nutrients from the soil.
His interest in photography absorbs him completely.
Her interest in butterflies absorbs her completely.
A black star absorbs all matter.
The walls are made of a material that absorbs sound.
Our oatmeal face mask absorbs impurities from your skin.
California absorbs many of the legal immigrants to the US.
Defence spending absorbs almost 20% of the country's wealth.
